{"tid":694179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片：十里無人　的士飄移稱避車","createTime":"2018-06-08T05:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T16:27:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7833c72cfc7c858fdd33e7a24932acb3e58dfe96","tid":694179,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180608/20414453\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F20414453&d=akJa0BhxT1CBrAKZ%2F%2FudKR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=e5b23b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180608%2F20414453&h=0e2cfeee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180608/20414453</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月08日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：十里無人　的士飄移稱避車<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180608/large/a1605a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180608%2Flarge%2Fa1605a.gif&h=e8aabd78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■紅的飄移至打橫停咗喺路中間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連日天雨路滑，揸車都真係要額外留神。好似前晚8點幾，西九龍走廊向尖沙嘴方向發生一單交通意外。有個的士司機揸住部紅的，唔知佢係唔係當的士係跑車，喺橋面行行吓突然玩起飄移上嚟，的士其後失控跣咗幾個車位後，就打橫停咗喺路中間。<br />\n<br />\n原本的哥打死火燈倒車，諗住掉頭走，點知尾隨一架紅頂小巴就駛到，結果避無可避，小巴司機收唔切，車頭直撞的士左邊車身。就係咁，的哥因為腰痛要送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n市民蔡先生喺附近大廈返緊工，佢話當時望落街就見到呢單意外。佢話好彩之後途經司機都收慢停車，唔係就大件事。警方指63歲姓陳的士司機同70歲姓吳小巴司機都冇飲酒，不過的哥就同阿Sir講，係閃避切線車輛失控出事喎，吓？閉路電視明明影到係佢自炒喎，當時的士附近都冇其他車。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片：三車串燒激到阿Sir扎扎跳<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n今日焦點‧即聽"},{"pid":"f14ee37fa66324f605576cea1045ab406a6b9111","tid":694179,"uid":3774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"唔通佢見到隱形戰車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cce937ffd75df2ee9472860adafd4e47579b19","tid":694179,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"小巴司機盲?"},{"pid":"69b0cbf849ddcab741b32757af8fbcfa66bc70ea","tid":694179,"uid":23635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:10:41.000Z","msg":"頭搖又尾擺，飄移境界"},{"pid":"5dfef2ffb70ffb9e8e61d5d91fa9cefc48bdc3f0","tid":694179,"uid":54228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"哼！用愛膚堅啦！"},{"pid":"1e80e1f828c30542acbeac62dea6d3cf48631434","tid":694179,"uid":5081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"咁個的士司機可能真係見到有車呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b04d37a9b4be6de2e6f8f973621cedac7ebac7","tid":694179,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:24:53.000Z","msg":"的哥?"},{"pid":"ed22b7d2c7fb1934fa2021eb8aae7eb2357fae38","tid":694179,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T06:31:59.000Z","msg":"哼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快極咪又係紅的"},{"pid":"fba84c7bf033102c716a435c861a0847959c4d35","tid":694179,"uid":168169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T16:27:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oX4DH0eMs84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoX4DH0eMs84&d=akJa0BhxT1CBrAKZ%2F%2FudKR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=119636cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oX4DH0eMs84</a>"}]}